    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A logic based on the idea that propositions can be graded in value, rather than simply being true or false. Fuzzy logic has applications in expert systems and artificial intelligence.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
